query:
INSERT IGNORE INTO island_spot_access (islandId, spotId, distanceKm, recommended, sortOrder)
SELECT ig.id as islandId, asp.id as spotId, NULL as distanceKm, 1 as recommended, 0 as sortOrder
FROM island_guides ig
JOIN activity_spots asp ON ig.id = asp.islandGuideId
WHERE asp.published = 1 AND ig.published = 1;
